          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Physical DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/02/25/35428890/d239457501846014cb4c545b50959bd9_1028446808563096986.png",
                "id": "talent95213",
                "key": "Favonius Bladework - Edel",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Favonius Bladework - Edel"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo DMG</span>. If this character has not yet gained <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Grimheart</span>, they will gain <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Grimheart</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Grimheart</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">After the character to which this is attached uses Icetide Vortex</span>: Remove this status, DMG +3 for this instance.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/02/25/35428890/78b526224710dda639b49972145339a9_2259309447152107260.png",
                "id": "talent84777",
                "key": "Icetide Vortex",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Icetide Vortex"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: #99FFFF\">Cryo DMG</span>, creates 1 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Lightfall Sword</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/02/25/35428890/72b7716be67efac4ec94efde16957180_3727750409446248840.png",
                "id": "talent83901",
                "key": "Glacial Illumination",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Glacial Illumination"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Lightfall Sword</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Summon</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When Eula uses a Normal Attack or Elemental Skill</span>, this card will accumulate 2 Zeal stacks, but Eula will not gain Energy.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">End Phase:</span> Discard this card and deal 3 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Physical DMG</span>.</p><p>Each Zeal stack adds 1 DMG to this damage instance.</p><p>(Effects on this card's <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage(s) </span>will apply to <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Zeal</span>.)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/02/25/35428890/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_5437320841983151191.png",
                "id": "talent60317",
                "key": "Lightfall Sword",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/02/26/35428890/3f07051befd3fcb50000df92021710d6_4405379057041270944.png",
                "title": "Lightfall Sword"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Applies Cryo and can trigger the following Elemental Reactions:</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Melt</span>: DMG +2 for this instance</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Superconduct</span>: DMG+1 for this instance, deal 1 Piercing DMG to all opposing characters except the target</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Frozen</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, the target is unable to perform any Actions this Round (Can be removed in advance after the target receives Physical or Pyro DMG, in which case they will take +2 DMG)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/02/25/35428890/4bcc4b82a9d7ee22770f60afa54e9919_2627537380589760044.png",
                "id": "talent58904",
                "key": "Cryo DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Cryo DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Physical DMG</span></strong></p><p>Physical DMG will not apply any Elements, nor can it engage in Elemental Reactions.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Usage(s)</span></strong></p><p>After this card's effect is triggered, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage </span>of it will be consumed.</p><p>This card will be discarded immediately once it has 0 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usages </span>remaining.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/02/25/35428890/1ece3cf73687b4b134d3d9027b718b40_772748918175435493.png",
